<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="virtue-n">virtue <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'vɜːtʃuː/    美 /'vɜːrtʃuː/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>美德；德行：</strong></h4>
<p>反 vice </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In modern society, punctuality is a necessary virtue.
在现代社会，守时是必不可少的美德。</p><footer>2015 陕西</footer></div>

<h4 id="2advantage">2.<strong>优点；长处(advantage)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One of his virtues is that he never gets angry.
他的一个优点是从不生气。</p></div></div>